Mixed-License Notice
====================

This repository is a Phase 1 research reproduction package. It contains a
mixture of original experiment materials, adapted code, and third-party code.
The repository as a whole should not be treated as being under a single
permissive license.

Summary
-------

1. PoisonedRAG-derived code

   Portions of this repository are adapted from PoisonedRAG:

   https://github.com/sleeepeer/PoisonedRAG

   PoisonedRAG is distributed under the MIT License. The original MIT notice is
   preserved below.

2. Contriever-derived code

   Files under:

   experiments/src/contriever_src/

   include code derived from the Contriever project:

   https://github.com/facebookresearch/contriever

   Contriever is distributed under Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial
   4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0). This means those components are limited to
   non-commercial use unless separate permission is obtained from the relevant
   rights holder.

   License URI:
   https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/legalcode

3. Other embedded notices

   Some individual files include their own copyright or license notices in file
   headers. Those notices remain in effect for those files.

4. New Phase 1 materials

   The Phase 1 experiment scripts, result tables, figures, and reports created
   for this reproduction package are provided for academic and research use.
   They do not relicense any third-party material included in this repository.

Practical Implication
---------------------

Academic reading, reproduction, and non-commercial research use are the intended
uses for this repository. Commercial reuse of the complete repository may be
restricted because of the Contriever-derived components.


